# AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.failed

**Case**

The object can no longer render sample buffers because of an error.

## Declaration

```swift
case failed
```

## Status values

- **AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.unknown**: The object doesn’t have any sample buffers enqueued.
- **AVQueuedSampleBufferRenderingStatus.rendering**: The object is rendering the sample buffer.
